OL,3,CParents of three-year-old girl with
OL,4,Crare cancer fundraising for new home
OL,6,FThe parents of a three-year-old girl
OL,7,Fwho has been left paralysed by a rare
OL,8,Fform of cancer are hoping to raise
OL,9,Fenough money to give her a properly
OL,10,Fadapted new home.
OL,12,FClara Gilley, from Plymouth, fell ill
OL,13,Fon her birthday earlier this year and
OL,14,Fis likely to lose the use of her arms
OL,15,Fand legs.
OL,17,FHer parents are by her side at Bristol
OL,18,FChildren's Hospital and are asking for
OL,19,Fthe public's help to build Clara's new
OL,20,Flife.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
