OL,3,CParents of three-year-old girl with
OL,4,Crare cancer fundraising for new home
OL,6,FHer dad Matthew Gilley said: "On her
OL,7,Fbirthday, which was Good Friday, she
OL,8,Fwasn't quite herself, her head was
OL,9,Fleaning to the side.
OL,11,F"On Easter Sunday, she was walking
OL,12,Faround the house just fine and then
OL,13,Fall of a sudden just stopped moving."
OL,15,FMatthew and his wife Alana called an
OL,16,Fambulance and the family was taken to
OL,17,FDerriford Hospital in Plymouth. It was
OL,18,Fthere that doctors found a rare type
OL,19,Fof cancerous tumour pressing against
OL,20,FClara's spine.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
