OL,3,CParents of three-year-old girl with
OL,4,Crare cancer fundraising for new home
OL,6,FShe was moved to Bristol Children's
OL,7,FHospital, where she has been ever
OL,8,Fsince, paralysed and undergoing
OL,9,Fchemotherapy and radiotherapy.
OL,11,FAlana said: "From very early on, we
OL,12,Fsort of knew that it was a possibility
OL,13,Fthat she might not regain any movement
OL,14,Fin her limbs at all.
OL,16,F"She's not necessarily going to get
OL,17,Fbetter from here. She might do, but a
OL,18,Flot of these things are unknown. You
OL,19,Fjust don't know what might come back,
OL,20,Fwhat might not.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
