OL,3,CParents of three-year-old girl with
OL,4,Crare cancer fundraising for new home
OL,6,F"But I think this is what life's going
OL,7,Fto be like, this is how she's going to
OL,8,Fbe."
OL,10,FThe next step is for the family to
OL,11,Fwork out where they are going to live,
OL,12,Fif and when Clara is well enough to
OL,13,Fleave the hospital.
OL,15,F"Our house is not a big house," said
OL,16,FAlana. "Without completely
OL,17,Freconfiguring our whole house, it
OL,18,Fwould not be possible to make it work
OL,19,Ffor somebody in a wheelchair.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
