OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1729262967
OL,3,CParents of three-year-old girl with
OL,4,Crare cancer fundraising for new home
OL,6,F"It's hard thinking life is just going
OL,7,Fto be really different.
OL,9,F"I think about all of her toys in the
OL,10,Fliving room, she's never going to be
OL,11,Fable to play with those in quite the
OL,12,Fsame way."
OL,14,FThe family are hoping to raise
OL,15,F#100,000 to find a bungalow that can
OL,16,Fbe adapted.
OL,18,FMatthew said: "I find it challenging,
OL,19,FI think we both do, to ask for
OL,20,Fdonations during what everybody is
OL,21,Ffinding a challenging time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
