OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F439A1729262967
OL,3,CParents of three-year-old girl with
OL,4,Crare cancer fundraising for new home
OL,6,F"We're finding it extra challenging,
OL,7,Ftrying to find a property that would
OL,8,Fbe suitable for Clara's needs. So I
OL,9,Falso find that a mental challenge as
OL,10,Fwell."
OL,12,FDespite everything, Matthew and Alana
OL,13,Fare trying to stay positive.J"I
OL,14,Fsuppose I see it now as this is like a
OL,15,Fnew chapter or new journey," Matthew
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,F"Although it is challenging, we are
OL,19,Fenjoying the moments we have because
OL,20,Fit's just part two of a great story
OL,21,Fthat is Clara.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
