OL,3,CParents of three-year-old girl with
OL,4,Crare cancer fundraising for new home
OL,6,F"She's bright, she's clever, she's
OL,7,Ffunny. You've got to remind yourself
OL,8,Fshe's three, so she has those three-
OL,9,Fyear-old tantrums at the same time
OL,11,F"She's worth the effort of getting her
OL,12,Fcured, because of how she is as a
OL,13,Fpersonality. Although it's
OL,14,Fchallenging, being around her is a
OL,15,Fjoy."
OL,17,FTo make a donation, visit the family's
OL,18,Ffundraising page.
